<b>Christine L. Borgman</b> (born 1951) is Professor and <university wordnetid="108286163" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../921/31921.xml">
University of California</link></university>
 Presidential Chair in Information Studies at the <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../844/1370844.xml">
Graduate School of Education and Information Studies</link>, <university wordnetid="108286163" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<ranking wordnetid="114429484" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../765/37765.xml">
University of California, Los Angeles</link></ranking>
</university>
. She was previously visiting professor at the <institute wordnetid="108407330" confidence="0.8">
<division wordnetid="108220714" confidence="0.8">
<administrative_unit wordnetid="108077292" confidence="0.8">
