<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../982/338982.xml">
Loughborough University</link></university>
, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../887/333887.xml">
Fulbright</link> Visiting Professor at the <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../820/1201820.xml">
Budapest University of Economic Sciences</link> and <link>
